Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.41,0:03:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒  太棒了
