Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇哉·布裡吉斯才是最棒的觸媒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Infinity1  聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
