Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.00,0:04:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了嗎  Argos1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.65,0:04:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正趕往你們那裡
